# Exclude node_modules at every depth, not just the repo root. Nested
# skills/*/node_modules can carry host-compiled native binaries (e.g.
# better-sqlite3) built for the host's Node ABI; leaking them into an image
# running a different Node major triggers NODE_MODULE_VERSION load errors.
# With these excluded, each skill's in-image `npm install` pulls the matching
# prebuilt binary instead.
**/node_modules
.git
.github
*.log
*.env
.env.*
!.env.example
test
docs
assets
README*.md
CHANGELOG.md
